				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Looking back, most of my professional work, both in programming and leadership, seems simple, even trivial. It’s important to remember, however, that a lot of it seemed dauntingly hard before I started the task at hand. I imagine most people can relate; in hindsight most problems seem trivial<sup><a href=\"#1\">1</a></sup>."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
