				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "rFSNSnLyDQCujclmCBR5Zw=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "In this post, I want to talk a bit about what I consider to be the hardest part: getting started. This is not a how-to guide, it is a collection of thoughts I had when taking a walk, so do not expect coming away from this any more enlightened than when you started out. At best, you will be inspired to get started on a project you’ve been looking at for a while, or reminded of a thing you learned a while ago but sometimes forget, just like I did."
			},
