				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2025-05-26T23:54:15.592354+02:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "CYvjqXLyDQCypLXiCBR5Zw=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "I’ve talked a bit about how it might be a hindrance to respect a problem *too much* now, but the opposite is also true. Most hard problems deserve respect, and the expectation should be that we will learn something new in the process."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2025-05-26T23:54:20.297163+02:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2025-05-27T00:04:45.831715+02:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "dT3wuXLyDQC5OEt9CBR5Zw=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Ironically, one of the things that makes both these learnings as well as just solving the problem is easier is keeping an open mind. The idea of “Beginner’s Mind” is now a bit of a trope, but it is truly important to not assume that we should know already, or that we do know. If we did, whatever we’re doing wouldn’t be a problem, and it certainly wouldn’t be hard."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2025-05-26T23:55:59.464219+02:00"
