				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "I’ve had my fair share of hard problems to think about in the last few years, not least in my work on [Glamorous Toolkit](https://gtoolkit.com/), but also in other projects that I’ve been spending time on in my work as a hired gun (that is why people hire me, after all), as well as in my personal life (two kids, and all the beautiful new experiences that they brought to my life) and even my hobbies (I’ve been picking up chess and keeping up with my physical practice, where I got certified as a Yoga teacher and placed squarely in the middle of the pack in a few streetlifting and powerlifting competitions)."
			},
